stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending_verification: User creates master profile
    
    pending_verification --> verified: Admin approves
    pending_verification --> banned: Admin rejects (fraud/spam)
    
    verified --> suspended: Violation detected
    verified --> banned: Serious violation
    
    suspended --> verified: Admin reinstates
    suspended --> banned: Repeated violations
    
    banned --> [*]
    
    note right of pending_verification
        Cannot create practices
        Profile hidden from users
        Waiting for admin review
        Documents submitted
    end note
    
    note right of verified
        Can create practices
        Visible to users
        Can accept bookings
        Normal operations
    end note
    
    note right of suspended
        Cannot create NEW practices
        Existing bookings remain
        Profile hidden
        Temporary ban
        Can appeal to admin
    end note
    
    note right of banned
        Cannot create practices
        All bookings cancelled
        Profile deleted from search
        Permanent ban
    end note
